1979;;Licensed to Love and Kill;;British;;Lindsay Shonteff;;Gareth Hunt, Fiona Curzon;;spy/action;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Licensed_to_Love_and_Kill;;Secret Agent Charles Bind is called in to investigate the disappearance of Lord Dangerfield, a British diplomat. The trail leads Bind to Dangefield’s daughter Carlotta Muff-Dangerfield who is called "Lotta Muff", an ambitious American Senator named Lucifer Orchid, and Bind’s counterpart in the forces of evil, Ultra One.